January 26, 2026, read second time, ordered engrossed. Engrossed.
January 27, 2026, read third time, passed. Yeas 36, nays 9.
HOUSE ACTION
January 29, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Public Policy.
February 10, 2026, reported — Do Pass.
