Mr. Speaker: Your Committee on Public Policy, to which was
referred Senate Bill 23, has had the same under consideration and begs
leave to report the same back to the House with the recommendation
that said bill do pass.
(Reference is to SB 23 as printed January 23, 2026.)
MANNING
Committee Vote: Yeas 9, Nays 1
